341
00:16:58,893 --> 00:17:00,143
What do you mean?
You just said that...

342
00:17:00,269 --> 00:17:01,645
I lied.

343
00:17:01,771 --> 00:17:03,855
I've been lying to you
in increasing amounts

344
00:17:03,981 --> 00:17:06,983
ever since I told you you looked
good unshaved a year ago.

345
00:17:07,110 --> 00:17:08,652
It's a little experiment,
you know,

346
00:17:08,778 --> 00:17:10,529
to see where you draw the line.

347
00:17:16,119 --> 00:17:16,993
How's the patient?

348
00:17:17,120 --> 00:17:18,620
Haven't been in yet, today.

349
00:17:18,746 --> 00:17:21,123
As long as he hasn't gotten
