long-distance carrier.

377
00:18:24,145 --> 00:18:25,312
Oh, I was right, wasn't I?

378
00:18:25,438 --> 00:18:28,148
Oh, yeah, it's always
about you, isn't it?

379
00:18:29,150 --> 00:18:31,030
He has the chills
